<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SMT News</title>

        /* Hide the sections by default */
        .news-section {
    /* Define CSS variables for colors */
    :root {
        --primary-color: #007bff;
        --primary-color-hover: #0056b3;
        --background-color: #f4f4f4;
        --text-color: #000;
        --ad-box-padding: 20px;
        --ad-box-margin: 20px 0;
        --ad-box-border-radius: 8px;
        --news-item-margin: 15px 0;
        --news-item-padding: 15px;
        --news-item-border-radius: 8px;
        --menu-button-padding: 10px 20px;
        --menu-button-font-size: 16px;
        --menu-button-margin: 5px;
        --menu-button-border-radius: 5px;
        --social-media-margin: 0 15px;
        --social-media-font-size: 24px;
    }

    /* Hide the sections by default */
    .news-section {
        display: none;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Active section will be shown with fade-in effect */
    .news-section.active {
        display: block;
        opacity: 1;
    }

    /* Ad Box Style */
    .ad-box {
        background-color: var(--background-color);
        padding: var(--ad-box-padding);
        margin: var(--ad-box-margin);
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: var(--ad-box-border-radius);
    }

    .ad-box p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    /* Social Media Links */
    .social-media {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .social-media a {
        margin: var(--social-media-margin);
        font-size: var(--social-media-font-size);
        color: var(--text-color);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Style for News Section */
    .news-item {
        margin: var(--news-item-margin);
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: var(--news-item-padding);
        border-radius: var(--news-item-border-radius);
    }

    /* Menu Style */
    .menu {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .menu button {
        padding: var(--menu-button-padding);
        font-size: var(--menu-button-font-size);
        margin: var(--menu-button-margin);
        cursor: pointer;
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: var(--menu-button-border-radius);
    }

    .menu button:hover {
        background-color: var(--primary-color-hover);
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .menu button {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    }

<body>
    <!-- Ad Box at the top of the page -->
    <div class="ad-box">
        <p><strong>Advertisement</strong></p>
        <p>Looking for amazing deals? Check out our partners!</p>
        <!-- Example Ad Code (could be an image, iframe, etc.) -->
        <a href="#" target="_blank"><img src="https://via.placeholder.com/468x60?text=Your+Ad+Here" alt="Ad" /></a>
    </div>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="SMT News Logo" width="150">
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Menu for Local, International, and Sports News -->
    <div class="menu">
        <button onclick="showNews('home')">Home</button>
        <button onclick="showNews('local')">Local News</button>
        <button onclick="showNews('international')">International News</button>
        <button onclick="showNews('sports')">Sports News</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Home Page News Section (automatically shown when the page loads) -->
    <section id="home-news" class="news-section active">
        <h2>Welcome to SMT News</h2>
        <p>Here are the latest headlines for you:</p>

        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>Local Event: Community Gathering</h3>
            <p>This community gathering aims to bring together local citizens...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>Global Summit: New Climate Agreement</h3>
            <p>World leaders have gathered to discuss the future of climate change...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>National Football League: New Record</h3>
            <p>The National Football League saw a new record in touchdowns...</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Local News Section -->
    <section id="local-news" class="news-section">
        <h2>Local News</h2>
        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>Local Event: Community Gathering</h3>
            <p>This community gathering aims to bring together local citizens...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>Local Development: New Park Opening</h3>
            <p>A new park is being opened in the downtown area...</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- International News Section -->
    <section id="international-news" class="news-section">
        <h2>International News</h2>
        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>Global Summit: New Climate Agreement</h3>
            <p>World leaders have gathered to discuss the future of climate change...</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sports News Section -->
    <section id="sports-news" class="news-section">
        <h2>Sports News</h2>
        <div class="news-item">
            <h3>National Football League: New Record</h3>
            <p>The National Football League saw a new record in touchdowns...</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Social Media Links -->
    <div class="social-media">
        <p>Follow us on:</p>
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
        <a href="https://www.twitter.com" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 SMT News. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // JavaScript function to show the corresponding news section
        function showNews(category) {
            // Hide all news sections
            const allSections = document.querySelectorAll('.news-section');
            allSections.forEach(section => {
                section.classList.remove('active');  // Remove active class
            });

            // Show the clicked category's news section
            const section = document.getElementById(category + '-news');
            if (category === 'home') {
                // Show Home News by default
                const homeSection = document.getElementById('home-news');
                homeSection.classList.add('active');
            } else {
                section.classList.add('active');  // Add active class to show section
            }
        }

        // Automatically show Home Page News on page load (this is the default visible section)
        window.onload = function() {
            showNews('home'); // Show Home News by default
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
